&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
先日の天龍寺の椿をクローズアップ。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Flowers" /><category term="Tenryu-ji" /><summary type="html">Closeup on a camellia, the other day at Tenryu-ji Temple.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2203_A7R05792.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2203_A7R05792.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">It‘s Starting・始まります</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220315/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="It‘s Starting・始まります" /><published>2022-03-15T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-03-15T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/starting</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220315/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    The first cherry blossoms are out in Kyoto. A few days of warm weather was all the incentive needed.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
京都では桜の開花が始まりました。数日の暖かい気候が、その気にさせたのでしょう。

  
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Cherry Blossoms" /><summary type="html">The first cherry blossoms are out in Kyoto. A few days of warm weather was all the incentive needed.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2203_A7R05802.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2203_A7R05802.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Tenryuji・天龍寺</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220314/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Tenryuji・天龍寺" /><published>2022-03-14T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-03-14T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/tenryuji</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220314/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
