&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
天龍寺の曹源池庭園と大方丈、マジックアワーの時間帯。
  
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Tenryu-ji" /><summary type="html">The Sogenchi Garden and main Hojo at Tenryuji Temple, in the late afternoon.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2203_A7R05780.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2203_A7R05780.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Ninenzaka・二年坂</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220312/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Ninenzaka・二年坂" /><published>2022-03-12T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-03-12T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/ninenzaka</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220312/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    Looking down Ninenzaka street during the Hanatouro Lantern Festival.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
  花灯路の二年坂の風景。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Higashiyama" /><category term="Kiyomizudera" /><category term="Night" /><category term="Lightup" /><summary type="html">Looking down Ninenzaka street during the Hanatouro Lantern Festival.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2203_A7R05638.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2203_A7R05638.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Komainu</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220311/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Komainu" /><published>2022-03-11T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-03-11T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/komainu</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220311/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
